title: Loving Hut Express - Food Cart
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Asian
description: Part of international chain of vegan restaurants opened by followers of Supreme Master Ching Hai, an advocate for veg living. Each location is individual family owned and operated. This one is a food cart that serves vegan food and drinks. Has kebabs, falafel, goulash, spring rolls, rice dishes, noodles. Previously parked at Askerceva 12-18.
